        <updateDate>2019-08-26T22:26:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Breaking Addiction Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill allows state Medicaid&nbsp;programs to provide medical assistance for community-based, inpatient, substance-use-disorder treatment services furnished in facilities&nbsp;with 60 or fewer beds&nbsp;to individuals&nbsp;between 21 and 65 years of age.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
